@anchor{pdf_noncentral_student_t}
@deffn {Function} pdf_noncentral_student_t (@var{x}, @var{n}, @var{ncp})

Returns the value at @var{x} of the density function of a noncentral Student 
random variable @math{nc_t(n,ncp)}, with @math{n>0} degrees of freedom and 
